Components Needed:
Arduino Board (e.g., Uno, Mega, etc.)
16x2 LCD Display (with I2C Backpack for Adafruit_LiquidCrystal library)
TMP36 Temperature Sensor
Jumper Wires
Breadboard (optional)


Hardware Connections
1. TMP36 Temperature Sensor
Vout (Middle Pin) ->Connect to Analog Pin A0 on Arduino.
GND (Left Pin) ->Connect to Arduino GND.
Vcc (Right Pin) -> Connect to Arduino 5V.
2. LCD with I2C Backpack
SDA Pin → Connect to Arduino A4 (Uno) or 20 (Mega).
SCL Pin → Connect to Arduino A5 (Uno) or 21 (Mega).
GND → Connect to Arduino GND.
Vcc → Connect to Arduino 5V.
